<br>
Vicious looked over to see Crowley standing where the wall Vicious had jumped through had been. He had taken the time to put some pants on, and looked pissed. Vicious was about to slam into Stein when he remebered that whole “Blast ya with Numina” thing. If Crowley could control that…<br>
<br>
Vicious ran forward three steps, activated Celerity once again, and jumped over Crowley, flipping in the air and landing facing Stein. Good thing this apartment had a high ceiling. Vicious landed, pulled his cigarettes out, and lit one.<br>
<br>
“Well, Lord Naughtius of the Tentacle Rape Society, you’re going to die now. Sorry.”<br>
<br>
Vicious noted a nearby chair, pulled a piece off, and turned….<br>
<br>
….and watched as Stein’s arrogant expression turned to one of shock, and then outright fear, but he didn’t run. Rather, he slowly backed away from Crowley, as though waiting for something….<br>
<br>
….that something very likely wasn’t two knives impaling his legs, two more impaling his arms, and a last one landing squarely in his neck. He reeled backward as Vicious blurred forward and slammed the chair leg into Stein’s heart, causing him to fall backwards onto the ground, incapacitated.<br>
<br>
“Booyah! Score one for me and Crowley!” Vicious smiled as he turned around, and then he noticed that Crowley seemed very spaced out.<br>
<br>
“Crowley! We won, you can stop trying to Dominate the air molecules now. “<br>
<br>
“Oh. Very good.”<br>
<br>
“Now grab a leg and help me drag this fucker so we can question him. And find me a blowtorch and some rubbing alcohol, stat!” <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.showPrevMessage?topicID=108.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.showNextMessage?topicID=108.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=108.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/prefabs/ez/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.threadControl?topicID=108.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/posticons/techops.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=108.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=108.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub98.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="scbnforum58570frm12">Blackjack's Message B